LogicalIdMapping is a BusinessClass
    owned by la
    prefix is LIDM
    stored in environment   

    Ontology
    	symbolic key is LogicalIdMapping

    Patterns    	
    	disable AuditIndex
		disable AsOfDateProcessing
		implements CRUD
		disable EffectiveDated

    Persistent Fields
    	LogicalId is Alpha size 250    		
    	DataArea
    	IONConnection
    	Active is Boolean
    	
    Derived Fields
    	UpperCaseDataArea is a DerivedField
			type is DataAreaName
			restricted
			return parentcontext.dataarea  
			
		Default is a NativeField
			type is Boolean
			      	
    	
    Field Rules
    	IONConnection
    		constraint (IONConnection.Usage.Outbox)
    			"InvalidIONConnection"
    			
		LogicalId
			constraint (LogicalId matches "[a-z0-9:\-/_\.]+")
				"InvalidLogicalIdFormat"
				
		DataArea
			default to UpperCaseDataArea
			initial value is UpperCaseDataArea
			
		Active
			default to true
			    	
    Sets
		ByDataArea
			no duplicates
			indexed
 			Sort Order
 				DataArea
 				IONConnection
			Instance Selection
				where (Active) 				

		ByLogicalId
			no duplicates
			indexed
			Sort Order
				LogicalId				
			Instance Selection
				where (Active)



		
	Actions
		Create is a Create Action
			restricted
		Update is an Update Action
			restricted
		Delete is a Delete Action
